    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is an absolute showroom-quality specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and presented in true 'time capsule' condition. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, complemented by pristine alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, and every electronic feature\u2014from the advanced navigation to the ambient lighting\u2014operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented service history with every interval performed at the dealership. With a spotless undercarriage and a detailed engine bay, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a collector-grade example that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
