      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single week. It looks and smells brand new\u2014seriously, not a single scratch or smudge anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream, and I\u2019ve taken care of every little detail so you don't have to. I\u2019m really looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Come by and take it for a spin, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love!",
