      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and M-Variable limited-slip differential. Maintenance is exhaustive: rod bearings replaced, VANOS system overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced for structural longevity. The suspension remains tight with OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the factory paint is flawless, and the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear. A collector-grade example of the ultimate driving machine.",
